lyTime":"2019-08-24T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"其實都係架。等於跑馬拉松，我叫你一次過跑42km大部份人都頂唔順，但如果我叫你逐k逐k咁跑，中間又有得抖有得食野飲水既，一定好好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd69918508cab643469de67e88b5f03e40a813d5","tid":1502573,"uid":59344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得港人容易滿足於呢啲定出嚟嘅勝利<br />\n就好似所謂階段性勝利<br />\n滿足咗內心嘅寄望就減低再走出嚟嘅意慾<br />\n未必係好事"},{"pid":"c17a936df710bb843939369cf13f2cc59fc0811b","tid":1502573,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a617ce36a115ffe5a7226649e6d89eec4a64ee","tid":1502573,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd69918508cab643469de67e88b5f03e40a813d5","tid":1502573,"uid":59344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得港人容易滿足於呢啲定出嚟嘅勝利<br />\n就好似所謂階段性勝利<br />\n滿足咗內心嘅寄望就減低再走出嚟嘅意慾<br />\n未必係好事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"會唔會係講出黎既方式可能再改善下?<br />\n<br />\nX 錯誤示範 X<br />\n林卓廷: 贏緊5:0 -&gt; 令人以為示威者佔上上風, 可以返屋企訓覺 (好彩無人信)<br />\nHOCC: 無催淚彈, 香港人贏左 (無催淚彈點解=勝利? 同埋無鼓勵同路人繼續爭取)<br />\n<br />\n小妹不才. 以下拋磚引玉:<br />\n823香港人再創造奇蹟, 感動左唔少同路人甚至係外國人<br />\n望落再膠再無可能既事都被香港人做到, <br />\n20多萬市民手拖手話比政府聽五大訴求, 缺一不可, <br />\n順住個勢, weekend大型活動繼續努力"},{"pid":"4a6c34c21a84aa3be4512a4b537b00df76e913b1","tid":1502573,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84jk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=e0d7bca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n懷疑受干擾 無理由日推夜推連登仔完成唔到"},{"pid":"e2425bab4d5c853e69102d15e4f908534248235a","tid":1502573,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:24:16.000Z","msg":"我一直支持階段性勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b15be376dc68b26eec0d635fa834cc6701a942a","tid":1502573,"uid":258703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"P牌想推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c188a7edc62cc9272e34fd744cc973ff06d1fd5b","tid":1502573,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b15be376dc68b26eec0d635fa834cc6701a942a","tid":1502573,"uid":258703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"P牌想推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:27:21.000Z","msg":"i know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d72177c19df129933acaf89ad045b761221915d","tid":1502573,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩個月前已經講緊<br />\n但有班人永遠覺得li次行動無實際成果=失敗<br />\n事實上 最成功兩日 812 823 都因為達成局部成果唔戀戰而成功<br />\n但都理解 塞爾維亞耐性同香港人耐性完全唔同層次<br />\n難聽D講句 香港人有一日唔流血都會有人話淡化左就黎輸<br />\n咁好難贏"},{"pid":"a905532e853adeab976c44e2f2ed98a55fdb12c4","tid":1502573,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:29:03.000Z","msg":"今天我"},{"pid":"a28b0df36e28fa7e191ebde7c7cc4f4f52613758","tid":1502573,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"662eaa36d63dd436b41cbcee1ac18383d433139a","tid":1502573,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以激勵士氣 但唔要階段勝利</span></span>"},{"pid":"e39b27d3f2ab3edaf6aee2e5fd10dc5f8c9ad61d","tid":1502573,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d72177c19df129933acaf89ad045b761221915d","tid":1502573,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩個月前已經講緊<br />\n但有班人永遠覺得li次行動無實際成果=失敗<br />\n事實上 最成功兩日 812 823 都因為達成局部成果唔戀戰而成功<br />\n但都理解 塞爾維亞耐性同香港人耐性完全唔同層次<br />\n難聽D講句 香港人有一日唔流血都會有人話淡化左就黎輸<br />\n咁好難贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"1. 忘記左邊位巴打呢幾日有篇文章, 話有時點解前線明知送頭都要去做<br />\n就係為左黑警會犯錯同keep住大家抗爭意志, 犧牲會成為種子 (大概意思, 唔係好記得)<br />\n為左場運動, 呢D犧牲能否避免? 有無成本更低既做法?<br />\n<br />\n2. 無大台容許好多不同創意, 我好認同「唔理得唔得, 做左先」<br />\n因為我地面對一個如此無恥既政府, 實在有必要試多D手法<br />\n正如巴打所講有班手足「永遠覺得li次行動無實際成果=失敗」,<br />\n抱有呢種心態絕對捱唔完呢場耐力戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慶祝小勝 =/= 今天我式I will be back</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們需要肯定每一次行動有其積極意義, 有助促成最終目標</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求, 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9207c4785cdaa8bc0f493f43695be5a005dffbc","tid":1502573,"uid":261113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:39:51.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}